import React from 'react';
import Entrance from './Entrance';

function Login() {
    return (
        <Entrance
            name="login"
            title="Вход"
            buttonTitle="Войти">

            <input
            className="login__input login__input_email"
            name="email"
            type="email"
            placeholder="Email"
            id="login__input_email"
            minLength="2"
            maxLength="40"
            required />

            <input
            className="login__input login__input_password"
            name="password"
            type="password"
            placeholder="Пароль"
            id="login__input_password"
            minLength="2"
            maxLength="40"
            required />
        </Entrance>

    )
}

export default Login;
